Who Am I?

Hi I'm Arnav Kasturia, an undegraduate CSE student at Arizona State University. I like participating in hackathons as it gives me a very good opportunity to get to know people with different backgrounds. It also gives me an experience of working as a team, coming up with new ideas and taking decisions when necessary. I see myself as a team player and a person with whom people would really enjoy working with.

I'm always trying to add things to my skillset and work consistently to get better at things I already know. I have a very good understanding of essential Data Structures and Algorithms which is not very common for someone just starting with their sophomore year.
